text: Agaue is a genus of arachnids in the family Halacaridae. There are at least four described species in Agaue. ==Species== * Agaue chevreuxi (Trouessart, 1889) * Agaue hamiltoni Womersley, 1937 * Agaue magellanica Newell, 1971 * Agaue marginata Viets, 1950 ==References== ==Further reading== * * Category:Trombidiformes
title: Agaue (arachnid)
